                "invention-title": [
                    "Preparation method of high-purity superfine rhenium powder",
                    "一种高纯超细铼粉的制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a preparation method of high-purity superfine rhenium powder. The preparation method comprises the following steps: 1) preparing rhenium trioxide powder: calcining and decomposing ammonium perrhenate to obtain the rhenium trioxide powder; 2) carbon thermal pre-reduction: mixing the rhenium trioxide powder obtained in the step 1) with carbon black, and then heating and pre-reducing in an inert gas atmosphere to obtain pre-reduced powder; and (3) hydrogen final reduction is conducted, specifically, the pre-reduced powder obtained in the step (2) is subjected to final reduction in the hydrogen atmosphere, and the superfine rhenium powder is obtained. The purity of the rhenium powder prepared through the method can be larger than 99.99%, the average particle size is as low as 108.6 nm, and compared with a traditional method for reducing ammonium rhenate through hydrogen, caking of the rhenium powder can be reduced, and the particle size of the rhenium powder can be reduced. According to the method, the rhenium powder is prepared in the mode of combining carbon thermal pre-reduction and hydrogen final reduction for the first time, the cost is low, the yield is high, and the requirement for preparing rhenium-containing products through a powder metallurgy method in the industry can be further met."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种高纯超细铼粉的制备方法，包括如下步骤：1)制备三氧化铼粉末：将高铼酸铵煅烧分解得到三氧化铼粉末；2)碳热预还原：将步骤1)得到的三氧化铼粉末与炭黑混合，然后在惰性气体气氛下加热预还原，得到预还原粉末；3)氢气终还原：将步骤2)得到的预还原粉末在氢气气氛下进行终还原，得到超细铼粉。采用本发明方法制备的铼粉纯度能大于99.99％，平均粒度低至108.6nm，与传统的氢还原铼酸铵方法相比，能够减少铼粉的结块，降低铼粉的粒径。本发明首次采用碳热预还原与氢气终还原相结合的方式制备铼粉，成本低产率高，能够进一步满足工业上粉末冶金法制备含铼产品的需求。"
                }
            ]
